projects.title: Radiation
projects.description: Stock exchange project enabling users to place and cancel orders with sub-millisecond latency, maintain user balances, and provide constant live streaming of the order book and trades. Architecture in microservices, leveraging cutting-edge technologies/ async communication between services. Containerised all components, Utilised message queue, Redis queue, Pub/Sub, and PostgreSQL TimeSeriesDB. In-memory orderbook processing for high-speed operations and in-parallel persisting order book mutations for consistency and reliability.

projects.title: Code Execution Engine
projects.description: Streamline your code execution with our remote engine that safely runs tasks in Docker containers, ensuring efficient and reliable results. Resilient to malicious program, infinite loop, recursive functions without exit condition. Resilient against Fork Bomb Manage CPU and memory heavy job. Collaborated with Minecraft server administrators to suggest features and get feedback about the plugin.

projects.title: Radiation - Distributed Stock Exchange System
projects.description:
Stock exchange project enabling users to place and cancel orders with sub-millisecond latency, maintain user balances, and provide constant live streaming of the order book and trades.

Features

  • Architecture in microservices, leveraging cutting-edge technologies/ async communication between services.
  • Containerised all components, Utilised message queue, Redis queue, Pub/Sub, and PostgreSQL TimeSeriesDB.
  • In-memory orderbook processing for high-speed operations and in-parallel persisting order book mutations for consistency and reliability.

Achieved order placing latency of less than a millisecond, ensuring fast and efficient transactions.

projects.title: Teapost
projects.description:
NewsPost Publishing Web App built from scratch using MERN stack and relevant 3rd party libs. This was the first project I built from myself which helped me to reach a point of inflection.


Features

  • Stories can be commented on, like or dislike, can create stories Collection like YouTube playlist for future reference alike YouTube playlist.
  • In-house Authentication and Authorisation and associated required features like forgot email/password, reset password, verify email.
  • Reader can follow authors, in-house user Image gallery hooked with cloudinary.
  • Write stories in collaboration with other authors.
  • In-house admin panel, allow admin to manage users and stories.
